OL,6,FA postman who murdered and decapitated
OL,7,Fhis 21-year-old girlfriend before
OL,8,Fsearching for internet pornography 170
OL,9,Ftimes has been jailed for life, with a
OL,10,Fminimum of 23 years.
OL,12,FEwan Methven, 27, murdered Phoenix
OL,13,FSpencer-Horn in the home they shared
OL,14,Fin East Kilbride, South Lanarkshire,
OL,15,Fon November 16 2024, after the couple
OL,16,Fordered a takeaway to their flat near
OL,17,FGlasgow.
OL,19,FIn the hours before the killing, Miss
OL,20,FSpencer-Horn had texted her mother to
OL,21,Fsay they were eating dinner.
