OL,6,FAround midnight, neighbours reported
OL,7,Fhearing "increased activity" in the
OL,8,Ftop-floor flat.
OL,10,FThe High Court in Glasgow was told
OL,11,Fthat Methven attacked Miss Spencer-
OL,12,FHorn, stabbing her 20 times, including
OL,13,F10 times in the face, before
OL,14,Fmutilating her body and severing her
OL,15,Fhead, the court heard.
