OL,6,FMethven had also strangled her,
OL,7,Fsearched for internet pornography 170
OL,8,Ftimes and made repeated attempts to
OL,9,Fbuy cocaine, before spending the
OL,10,Fweekend driving around in Miss Spencer-
OL,11,FHorn's red Corsa, and texting her
OL,12,Fmother pretending she was still alive,
OL,13,Faccording to prosecutors.
OL,15,FOn the day of the murder, Methven had
OL,16,Fsent a message to his partner of two
OL,17,Fyears, saying that her waitress shifts
OL,18,Fmade him "lonely", the court heard.
