OL,6,FMiss Spencer-Horn was described as
OL,7,Fbeing in "good spirits" by colleagues
OL,8,Fat a hotel where she worked, and had
OL,9,Freplied to her boyfriend apologising,
OL,10,Fthe court heard.
OL,12,FAfter the murder, Methven ` who had
OL,13,Fmet his partner at a family party `
OL,14,Ftexted Miss Spencer-Horn's mother,
OL,15,FAlison Spencer, pretending to be her.
OL,17,FHe texted: "Hey sorry I've just woken
OL,18,Fup xxx" before searching for
OL,19,Fpornography, the court heard.
