OL,6,FOn November 18, at about midday, he
OL,7,Fdialled 999 and told a call-handler:
OL,8,F"I had a psychotic break and killed my
OL,9,Fwife."
OL,11,FHe said: "We were messing about, I
OL,12,Ftake steroids and was taking cocaine
OL,13,Fand alcohol, I think there was
OL,14,Fsomething else in it ... it was
OL,15,Ff****** horrible."
