OL,6,FHe was transferred to a senior police
OL,7,Fofficer, and said: "I just want to go
OL,8,Fto jail", and added: "I have been out
OL,9,Fmy face, I can't remember what
OL,10,Fhappened. I have been driving about
OL,11,Fall weekend."
OL,13,FPolice officers discovered Miss
OL,14,FSpencer-Horn's mutilated body hidden
OL,15,Funder a towel. Methven admitted
OL,16,Fattempting to remove the limbs and
OL,17,Ftorso from her body with a knife or
OL,18,Fother instrument.
