OL,6,FProsecutor Christopher McKenna
OL,7,Fpreviously said that on November 17,
OL,8,FMethven accessed pornography from
OL,9,Fabout 8am until about 6.30pm and was
OL,10,Fnoted to have accessed a pornographic
OL,11,Fvideo site 170 times, according to
OL,12,Fforensic analysis.
OL,14,FMethven pleaded guilty to murder and
OL,15,Fattempting to defeat the ends of
OL,16,Fjustice at the High Court in Glasgow.
OL,18,FThe court heard he had no previous
OL,19,Fconvictions and, on Monday, he was
OL,20,Fjailed for 23 years after appearing by
OL,21,Fvideolink at the High Court in Glasgow.
