OL,6,FDefending, Tony Graham KC, said, in
OL,7,F2024, Methven realised he had an
OL,8,Faddiction problem, and had written a
OL,9,Fletter to the judge saying "in
OL,10,Frelation to the harm that could cause,
OL,11,Fit could only be harm to himself",
OL,12,Fregarding cocaine, steroids and other
OL,13,Fdrugs.
OL,15,FMr Graham read from the letter, which
OL,16,Fsaid: "I know how loved Phoenix was
OL,17,Fand how she made her family complete.
OL,18,FI can't believe I've taken her from
OL,19,Fthem."
