OL,6,F"For reasons no-one will ever
OL,7,Funderstand, you strangled her and
OL,8,Fstabbed her 20 times, including 10 in
OL,9,Fthe face. You robbed her of all
OL,10,Fdignity in death by decapitating her
OL,11,Fand trying to dismember her.
OL,13,F"For two days after, you indulged in
OL,14,Fdrug abuse and watching pornography,
